Interface Dequeue<E>

Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements held in this deque
All Superinterfaces:
Collection<E>, Iterable<E>, Iterable<E>, Queue<E>
All Known Implementing Classes:
LinkedList
interface Dequeue<E> extends Queue<E>
A double-ended queue (deque) is a linear collection that supports element insertion and removal at both ends.
